column1: Que 2. Identify peak booking months and analyze reasons for spikes in bookings, including holidays or events?

column13: 1. Peak Booking Months: August, July & May

column4:
SELECT 
    arrival_date_month, 
    COUNT(booking_id) AS total_bookings
FROM booking_details
GROUP BY arrival_date_month
ORDER BY total_bookings DESC;

column6:
SELECT 
    arrival_date_year,
    arrival_date_month,
    arrival_date_day_of_month,
    COUNT(booking_id) AS total_bookings
FROM booking_details
GROUP BY arrival_date_year, arrival_date_month, arrival_date_day_of_month
ORDER BY total_bookings DESC;
